  "type": "feat",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 3rd level, the mesmerist can help allies shake off harmful conditions—especially those that affect their minds—by channeling psychic energy through his healing hands. He can use touch treatment a number of times per day equal to 3 + his Charisma modifier. Using the ability is a standard action (or a swift action if the mesmerist uses it on himself ), and the mesmerist must be able to touch his target. He can remove one condition from one target each time he uses this ability.</p>\n<p>At 3rd level, he can remove any condition on the minor conditions list.</p>\n<p><em>Minor Conditions:</em>&nbsp;Fascinated, shaken.</p>\n<p>At 6th level, he can remove any condition on the minor or moderate conditions list.</p>\n<p><em>Moderate Conditions:</em>&nbsp;Confused, dazed, frightened, sickened.</p>\n<p>At 10th level, he can remove any condition on the minor, moderate, or greater conditions list.<br><br><em>Greater Conditions</em>: Cowering, nauseated, panicked, stunned.<br><br>A 14th level, the mesmerist can instead expend one use of touch treatment to replicate the effects of break enchantment. This targets only one creature the mesmerist is touching and follows all other restrictions of touch treatment.</p>",
